{"tid":1689224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請投訴無綫新聞失實報道","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:58:37.000Z","uid":273953,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc46edaea27be61a064fb8af2adf8496c90a6b5","tid":1689224,"uid":273953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"請投訴無綫新聞失實報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=492df223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n投訴內容類別：節目<br />\n名稱：無綫新聞<br />\n日期：2019年11月3日<br />\n時間：00:06<br />\n本地電視節目服務：83台 (要「新增」) <br />\n投訴事項：<br />\n無綫新聞報道愛丁堡廣場及遮打花園集會被警方強行中止時，指警方於集會開始後一小時通知主辦方，實際上是警方於5時10分(集會開始10分鐘)已告知主辦方，要求集會於5時30分解散，當時集會和平進行，無綫新聞卻將示威者掟氣油彈及設路障片段加插其中。請跟進無綫新聞失實報道，企圖將警方無理打壓和平集會合理化。<br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=145496120170574&amp;id=118899846163535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D145496120170574%26id%3D118899846163535&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpP8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=4560c0e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=145496120170574&amp;id=118899846163535</a>"},{"pid":"ed6f9a37c1f28051e89a3a8b9a86c1769309fb4c","tid":1689224,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"0c90647b425e8b941176dc